docs {
  # Atlas Agents API

  This collection targets the Atlas `/agents` module.

  Notes:
  - Data routes use `Authorization: Bearer {{token}}`.
  - Data routes include the active tenant in the path.
  - `02-create-agent` stores returned `id` into `agentId`.
  - Update uses full replacement shape: `name`, `description`, `prompt`, `tools`, and `skills`.
}
